### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
### CREATE OPERATIONS (POST)
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════

@base = http://localhost:4004/library

### 1.1 Create an Author
POST {{base}}/Authors
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Dan",
  "lastName": "Brown",
  "nationality": "American",
  "email": "dan.brown@example.com",
  "isActive": true
}

### 1.2 Create a Book
POST {{base}}/Books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "The Da Vinci Code",
  "isbn": "9780307474278",
  "pages": 450,
  "price": 499.99,
  "publishedDate": "2024-01-01",
  "language": "English",
  "edition": 1,
  "totalCopies": 20,
  "availableCopies": 20,
  "summary": "Mystery thriller novel",
  "author_ID": "PASTE-AUTHOR-ID-HERE"
}

### 1.3 Create another Book
POST {{base}}/Books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Angels & Demons",
  "isbn": "9780743493468",
  "pages": 400,
  "price": 399.99,
  "publishedDate": "2024-02-01",
  "language": "English",
  "edition": 1,
  "totalCopies": 15,
  "availableCopies": 15,
  "summary": "Thriller novel",
  "author_ID": "PASTE-AUTHOR-ID-HERE"
}

### 1.4 Create with missing required fields
POST {{base}}/Books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "price": 99.99
}

### 1.5 Create with wrong data type
POST {{base}}/Books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Bad Data Book",
  "price": "not-a-number"
}

### ═══════════════════════════════════════
### READ OPERATIONS
### ═══════════════════════════════════════

### 2.1 Read all books
GET {{base}}/Books

### 2.2 Read single book
GET {{base}}/Books(1a2b3c4d-1111-1111-1111-111111111111)

### 2.3 Read a book that doesn't exist
GET {{base}}/Books(00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000)

### 2.4 Deep read: Get the author of a specific book
GET {{base}}/Books(1a2b3c4d-1111-1111-1111-111111111111)/author

### 2.5 Deep read: Get all books of an author
GET {{base}}/Authors(a1a1a1a1-aaaa-aaaa-aaaa-aaaaaaaaaaaa)/books

### 2.6 Read with expand
GET {{base}}/Books?$expand=author&$select=title,price


### ═══════════════════════════════════════
### UPDATE OPERATIONS
### ═══════════════════════════════════════

### 3.1 PATCH: Update only the price
PATCH {{base}}/Books(1a2b3c4d-1111-1111-1111-111111111111)
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "price": 699.99
}

### 3.2 PATCH: Update totalCopies and availableCopies
PATCH {{base}}/Books(1a2b3c4d-1111-1111-1111-111111111111)
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "totalCopies": 15,
  "availableCopies": 12
}

### 3.3 Verify the update
GET {{base}}/Books(1a2b3c4d-1111-1111-1111-111111111111)

### 3.4 PUT: Full replacement
PUT {{base}}/Books(1a2b3c4d-1111-1111-1111-111111111111)
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "SAP CAP Guide - Special Edition",
  "isbn": "9781234567890",
  "pages": 450,
  "price": 799.99,
  "publishedDate": "2025-01-01",
  "language": "English",
  "edition": 2,
  "totalCopies": 20,
  "availableCopies": 18,
  "summary": "Updated special edition of SAP CAP guide."
}

### 3.5 Verify after PUT
GET {{base}}/Books(1a2b3c4d-1111-1111-1111-111111111111)

### 3.6 Update a non-existent record
PATCH {{base}}/Books(00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000)
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "price": 99.99
}

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
### DELETE OPERATIONS
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════

### 4.1 Delete a book
DELETE {{base}}/Books(1a2b3c4d-1111-1111-1111-111111111111)

### 4.2 Verify it's gone
GET {{base}}/Books(1a2b3c4d-1111-1111-1111-111111111111)

### 4.3 Try to delete again (should return 404)
DELETE {{base}}/Books(1a2b3c4d-1111-1111-1111-111111111111)

### 4.4 Try to delete from read-only service
DELETE http://localhost:4004/reports/AvailableBooks(1a2b3c4d-1111-1111-1111-111111111111)

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
### @readonly ENFORCEMENT
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════

@reports = http://localhost:4004/reports

### 5.1 READ works on reports
GET {{reports}}/BookPricing

### 5.2 CREATE blocked on reports
POST {{reports}}/BookPricing
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Test",
  "price": 1.00
}

### 5.3 UPDATE blocked on reports
PATCH {{reports}}/BookPricing(2a2b3c4d-2222-2222-2222-222222222222)
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "price": 999.99
}

### 5.4 DELETE blocked on reports
DELETE {{reports}}/BookPricing(2a2b3c4d-2222-2222-2222-222222222222)

